            <title>[SPARK-3612] Executor shouldn&apos;t quit if heartbeat message fails to reach the driver</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3612</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
